always talkin' 'bout her.

555
00:25:10.009 --> 00:25:11.761
Seem like she always
up in the mix somehow.

556
00:25:11.928 --> 00:25:14.096
That's because
she's a fuckin' plague.

557
00:25:14.847 --> 00:25:18.184
Like an infection that-
that lingers and festers.

558
00:25:18.976 --> 00:25:21.479
