we can't hit her directly.

560
00:25:23.731 --> 00:25:25.691
She's got protection
from Manhattan.

561
00:25:26.442 --> 00:25:28.486
But we can fuck up her supply.

562
00:25:29.070 --> 00:25:30.988
And if she can't earn.

563
00:25:31.155 --> 00:25:32.782
she ain't worth lookin' after

564
