565
00:25:34.909 --> 00:25:38.371
Kanan sayin' Raq usin' hos
to move product in the city.

566
00:25:38.537 --> 00:25:40.206
Yeah. I'm-I'm aware.

567
00:25:40.373 --> 00:25:41.999
I'll handle that piece of it.

568
00:25:43.000 --> 00:25:45.294
Don't take this
the wrong way. Mr. Marchetti.

569
00:25:45.795 --> 00:25:48.256
