have to do with our work?

570
00:25:49.548 --> 00:25:52.260
I mean. we up in Queens while
she fuckin' wit' Manhattan.

571
00:25:52.426 --> 00:25:55.846
I don't care if she's in
Tipperary or Timbuk-fuckin'-tu.

572
00:25:56.013 --> 00:25:57.265
She tried to kill me.

573
00:25:57.431 --> 00:25:59.016
She's gotta answer for that.

574
00:25:59.976 --> 00:26:01.394
