598
00:27:09.962 --> 00:27:11.130
And I don't even wanna know.

599
00:27:11.297 --> 00:27:13.215
Either way.
this shit's fucked up.

600
00:27:13.382 --> 00:27:16.761
♪ You ain't gotta love me ♪

601
00:27:16.927 --> 00:27:19.096
♪ I just wanna know ♪

602
00:27:19.263 --> 00:27:20.723
