606
00:27:28.814 --> 00:27:32.610
♪ I'll let you stay
If you do me right ♪

607
00:27:32.777 --> 00:27:35.863
♪ Do me right ♪

608
00:27:36.030 --> 00:27:38.908
-[indistinct chatter]
-[siren wailing in distance]

609
