Why don't you take some glazed
home to the fam?

610
00:27:52.505 --> 00:27:54.048
That's the rest
of what she owes you.

611
00:27:55.549 --> 00:27:56.884
It's about fuckin' time.

612
00:27:58.302 --> 00:27:59.595
I wasn't gon' get involved.

613
00:28:00.179 --> 00:28:02.056
it's my daughter's deal.
not mine. but...

614
00:28:03.057 --> 00:28:05.118
