all your money now.

616
00:28:07.144 --> 00:28:08.813
Tell me what you know
about Famous.

617
00:28:11.273 --> 00:28:13.025
Nothin' more than
what's already out there.

618
00:28:14.193 --> 00:28:15.903
He disappeared
and then his body turned up.

619
00:28:16.070 --> 00:28:17.405
No idea who did it or why.

620
