642
00:29:16.755 --> 00:29:18.424
I hope it's gon' be
worth your money.

643
00:29:18.757 --> 00:29:19.757
That cop.

644
00:29:20.509 --> 00:29:22.636
better hope it's gon' be
worth my money.

645
00:29:27.475 --> 00:29:29.310
