in the not too distant future.

670
00:30:37.253 --> 00:30:40.381
I'm quite certain
he'll make his move.

671
00:30:40.965 --> 00:30:42.216
Fear not. though.

672
00:30:43.092 --> 00:30:45.344
I'll get to him
before he gets to me.

673
00:30:46.262 --> 00:30:47.471
I always do.

674
