678
00:31:01.026 --> 00:31:02.403
I ain't checkin' him like that.

679
00:31:02.945 --> 00:31:06.740
Ohh. what a tangled web
we weave.

680
00:31:08.033 --> 00:31:09.577
So Kanan is in league.

681
00:31:09.743 --> 00:31:13.956
