685
00:31:20.170 --> 00:31:21.797
that's fuckin' wit' my focus.

686
00:31:23.173 --> 00:31:24.173
Look...

687
00:31:24.383 --> 00:31:25.593
Kanan a damn kid.

688
00:31:26.302 --> 00:31:28.804
He just figured out how to tie
his own fuckin' shoes last week.

689
00:31:28.971 --> 00:31:31.181
If I ain't worried about him.
you shouldn't be neither.

690
00:31:32.433 --> 00:31:37.688
If-If I may offer a piece
of unsolicited advice.

691
00:31:38.606 --> 00:31:41.150
