of family secrets.

695
00:31:50.909 --> 00:31:52.161
And that's not good.

696
00:31:52.703 --> 00:31:54.121
For you or me.

697
00:31:54.538 --> 00:31:55.998
I'm keepin' an eye on him.

698
00:31:56.165 --> 00:31:59.001
Ohh. if I were you. I'd be
