699
00:31:59.168 --> 00:32:00.836
than just keepin' an eye on him.

700
00:32:03.714 --> 00:32:04.923
You got kids?

701
00:32:10.304 --> 00:32:11.930
Two boys and a girl.

702
00:32:13.474 --> 00:32:14.474
Older. though.

703
