So you know how these kids
always actin' out.

704
00:32:16.769 --> 00:32:18.854
tryin' to make space
between them and they parents.

705
00:32:19.355 --> 00:32:20.635
They gotta fuck shit up wit' you

706
00:32:20.689 --> 00:32:22.608
so they can feel like
they grown.

707
00:32:23.233 --> 00:32:25.361
