or not doin' the fuckin' dishes.

710
00:32:32.034 --> 00:32:33.869
It's a very different
proposition

711
00:32:34.036 --> 00:32:36.288
than Kanan working
with the cocksucker

712
00:32:36.455 --> 00:32:37.873
that wants you dead!

713
00:32:38.165 --> 00:32:39.541
I'm not takin' out my son.

714
00:32:39.708 --> 00:32:41.428
if that's what you gettin' at.
Mr. Bernardi.

715
00:32:42.211 --> 00:32:43.879
Not for you or nobody else.

716
00:32:44.380 --> 00:32:45.923
[dramatic music playing]

717
00:32:46.048 --> 00:32:48.759
Who said anything
about takin' him out?

718
00:32:51.136 --> 00:32:52.596
I'm just saying

719
00:32:53.263 --> 00:32:54.515
