730
00:33:33.762 --> 00:33:34.930
The kind of business

731
00:33:35.097 --> 00:33:36.932
that ain't nobody else business.

732
00:33:40.394 --> 00:33:41.770
I'm not a dummy. Kanan.

733
00:33:42.438 --> 00:33:43.564
I know you into some shit

734
00:33:43.731 --> 00:33:45.091
and I knew it
right when I met you.

735
00:33:45.691 --> 00:33:46.942
